"stránok a uloží všetky URL adresy do databázy. Plugin zaistí, že vaša cache "
"bude vždy načítaná vopred."

#: inc/Engine/Admin/Settings/Page.php:1137
msgid "Preload Links"
msgstr "Vopred načítať odkazy"

#. translators: %1$s = opening <a> tag, %2$s = closing </a> tag.
#: inc/Engine/Admin/Settings/Page.php:1140
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Link preloading improves the perceived load time by downloading a page when "
"a user hovers over the link. %1$sMore info%2$s"
msgstr ""
